title: 81. Manifesting Dreams Into Reality Ft. David Meltzer & Carlos Reyes
itunes:title: 81. Manifesting Dreams Into Reality Ft. David Meltzer & Carlos Reyes
description: Do you know your thoughts, both positive and negative, are responsible for your reality? On today's episode, Andy and his guests, David Meltzer and Carlos Reyes, discuss the opportunities in America, facing your biggest fears, and how to manifest your vision into a reality.
